These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: baking, cooking
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: crime, spy
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cycling, surfing
The people use 2 different means of transport: jet-ski, taxi
1. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the person who's sport is surfing##3
2. the person who's hobby is cooking is in an even position##4
3. the person watching spy movies is the person who's hobby is baking##1
4. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Hobby      | baking  | cooking   |
| Movie-Genre   | spy     | crime   |
| Sport         | surfing | cycling |
| Transport     | jet-ski | taxi    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different nationalities: italian, french
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, documentary
2 different pets are kept: dog, rat
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, tram
1. the owner of the rat is in an odd position##4
2. the person watching action movies is the person driving the tram##1
3. the french is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Nationality          | italian     | french |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | action  |
| Pet           | rat         | dog     |
| Transport     | motorbike   | tram    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, soy-milk
There 2 different types of food: lime, zucchini
2 different pets are kept: frog, lizard
The people use 2 different means of transport: bike, helicopter
1. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the person eating zucchini##3
2. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the person eating zucchini##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| Beverage    | soy-milk     | hot-chocolate |
| Food         | zucchini | lime    |
| Pet         | frog         | lizard        |
| Transport   | bike         | helicopter    |

