.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, sprite
There 2 different types of food: strawberry, zucchini
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: april, october
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: classical, pop
1. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
2. the person eating zucchini is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the fan of pop is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Beverage      | sprite     | almond-milk |
| Food          | zucchini   | strawberry  |
| Birthday         | april | october     |
| Music-Genre   | classical  | pop         |

